d half of the year. We believe that we are able to manage the seasonal fluctuations in milk procurement and production through our extensive procurement network and storage facilities.

## Raw Materials

We procure raw milk from milk farmers and through chilling centres and bulk coolers. We also procure packaging materials, such as poly pouches, Tetra Pak bricks, glass bottles, plastic bottles, cups, and other packaging materials from various vendors. We procure cattle feed, veterinary medicines, and other inputs required for our manufacturing operations from various vendors. We believe that we have adequate arrangements for the procurement of raw materials and other inputs required for our manufacturing operations.

## Marketing and Distribution

We have a structured pan-India distribution network to cater to our retail and institutional customers. We sell our products through a network of distributors, super stockists, and direct sales personnel. We also sell our products through modern trade outlets, including supermarkets and hypermarkets. We believe that our extensive distribution network enables us to reach a wide range of customers across India.

## Competition

The Indian dairy industry is highly fragmented and competitive. We compete with other dairy companies, both large and small, as well as with unorganized players. We believe that our key competitive strengths include our strong brand recognition, extensive distribution network, high-quality products, and experienced management team.

## Government Regulations

The dairy industry in India is regulated by various central and state government agencies. We are required to comply with various laws and regulations relating to food safety, quality standards, environmental protection, and labor laws. We believe that we are in compliance with all applicable laws and regulations.

## Human Resources

As of August 31, 2015, we had 1,572 employees. We believe that we have good relations with our employees and that our employees are well-trained and experienced. We provide various benefits to our employees, including health insurance, provident fund, and gratuity.

## Risk Factors

Investing in our shares involves a high degree of risk. Investors should carefully consider the risks described in this section, together with the other information contained in this Draft Red Herring Prospectus, before deciding to invest in our shares.

